Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My melons!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:03.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:07.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.40,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This is imprisonment!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:12.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,A beating!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:15.91,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,It's toy abuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:20.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out of this jail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.72,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Give me freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.28,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to think I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:29.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,making a scene by myself again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.58,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.38,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to stay cooped up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,in this crappy, cramped and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.21,0:00:38.25,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,filthy room of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:41.64,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Life was good while you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:43.41,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,were away in Hueco Mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I could pick up girls, stalk them,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.56,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,and do anything I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.49,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the reason why people outside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:55.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,are giving me dirty looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:15.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Unseasonal watermelons
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:19.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,are my favorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:54.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.07,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My...my pretty melons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.21,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!\NMelons...melons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to go out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.33,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Excuse me.\NMy melons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.88,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I heard that Karakura Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.29,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,was somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:14.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Go back the way you came,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.87,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,turn left where the roads cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,and then go straight and you'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.22,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.12,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.05,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My pretty melons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.07,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.14,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If she sees you, it won't be a laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.24,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:46.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, look after things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.38,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.47,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Behave yourself, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.64,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.55,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.42,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Another weird sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.70,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.29,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect me to behave myself at home
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.66,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,on such a fine day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.99,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.39,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt the joy and excitement of youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:38.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.18,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,It's that voluptuous babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.77,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.42,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:35.01,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody...somebody! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.62,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.49,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.56,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, this body doesn't belong to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,so catching a cold is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.45,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.81,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.08,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:01.80,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.07,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you asking directions earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:06.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,How did you end up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.12,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.76,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I see things that other people can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.98,B2,HARUKO (i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ken, I'm home! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.75,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, I lost my way, so I got back late! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:23.44,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make lunch right away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.90,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here you go! Thanks for being patient! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:30.39,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you think? Is it good, Ken? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.31,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Yup. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.14,B2,HARUKO(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, guess what! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:37.29,B2,HARUKO(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ken, I just saw someone flying in a black kimono! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.75,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Someone in a black kimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:43.48,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.48,0:06:44.68,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:47.66,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a ghost or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:48.95,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.72,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to see things like that since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.30,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:01.12,B2,HARUKO(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ken, after this, why don't we... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.21,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.65,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:10.90,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's end our relationship. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.26,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.90,B2,KEN	(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, you see people that others can't see, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.85,B2,KEN	(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and you talk to people who aren't there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:19.88,B2,KEN	(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}You're a great cook, {\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.99,B2,KEN	(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you kind of give me the creeps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:31.97,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see ghosts because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.15,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,And Ken told me he was leaving me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.94,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,after he finished eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:38.20,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.07,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Well yes, but I don't think before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:43.48,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,or after he eats really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:44.93,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:45.94,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:51.13,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on living after breaking up with Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.20,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Blond-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.67,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for rescuing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.37,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to gain by dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:00.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, the Hollows will come after you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.48,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,and going to the Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.82,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,isn't all that great either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.26,B2,CHILD,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I don't see a Hollow anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.62,B2,RUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.87,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Look there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Did a Hollow do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.67,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,No. An ordinary Hollow would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.76,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,only go after human souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.68,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not a Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.48,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Let's not be hasty, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.13,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:09.23,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,There have been five identical incidents such as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:10.81,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Five?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:11.99,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Society has been on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.91,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,special alert for cases like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:20.88,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiritual Pressure of the Hollow believed to be responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:24.23,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,for the incidents appears and disappears with each event,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.87,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,making it extremely difficult to track it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:32.00,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,But this body died very recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.97,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The victim's attacker couldn't have gone very far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.66,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, our priority is to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,stop the next attack before it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.35,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go on ahead and chase after the attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:45.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.41,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you after I turn over this crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.53,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:50.95,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Now get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:51.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.59,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.83,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,After all I did for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.91,B2,KEN	(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm home. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.83,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome home, Ken! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.72,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enjoy your dinner! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.04,B2,KEN(i),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! I sure will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.16,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.37,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm dead, I know you're going to regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:32.23,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.30,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.45,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,grant you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.22,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.13,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.26,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.34,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I will let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.73,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,So you can feel a Hollow's Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.56,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.60,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're not human?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:17.15,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm just temporarily borrowing this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.22,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.93,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I'm offering to grant your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.16,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,of wanting to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:27.65,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:30.62,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I have to prepare myself for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.75,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,What a silly thing to be concerned about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.12,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,when you're about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.66,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, there's no need to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.05,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,The pain is only momentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.51,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.43,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.51,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.30,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,So I can do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.48,B2,HANDSOME FELLOW,0000,0000,0000,,this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.45,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.33,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:10.50,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Now open your mouth wider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.83,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I will leech on to you and then suck out your nutrients!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:17.04,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I did to that dead man there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.84,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Kon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.63,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Kon Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,What're you waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.22,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:29.97,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:35.40,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,The Hollow's Spiritual Pressure disappeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:44.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,We should be safe for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.91,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What was that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.76,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.30,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.79,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.20,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,A monster that attacks people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.79,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,and sucks out their souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.07,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,But back there, he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.07,0:12:58.99,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand it myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.16,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,but I think he's an unusual type
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:02.92,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,that uses humans as his host.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.24,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.81,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:07.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:09.76,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.93,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.06,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:15.59,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't saved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.40,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I could have died right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:20.40,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you just leave me alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.76,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:27.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about wanting to die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.83,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who was killed back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:41.80,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee he didn't want to die that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.76,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Blond-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.22,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an ordinary human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.58,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,And to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.39,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to be disposed and killed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,But even I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.15,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,So don't talk like you want to die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.13,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.33,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:12.52,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.42,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.29,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,And I want you to promise me that you won't die either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.31,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Blond-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:25.85,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.48,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.39,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.36,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.97,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:51.03,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.53,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:56.00,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,I want to start over with you, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.46,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Because your meals are really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.11,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Is it too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.42,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.37,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:10.12,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.86,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.05,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:15.94,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.01,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.64,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.86,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.96,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Well, guess that means things aren't going
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:33.47,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,to work out with that voluptuous babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.74,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.11,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:41.21,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go home and do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.59,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.49,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:08.48,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Hollow make you its host?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.54,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Dar...ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.09,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, when did you enter her body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:37.55,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW),0000,0000,0000,,I just got a little lucky, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.42,B2,HARUKO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After you knocked me down and left me there {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:44.41,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW),0000,0000,0000,,I happened to run into that fatso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.52,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.59,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go..?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:55.95,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Then that Ken guy I saw earlier, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.91,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW),0000,0000,0000,,She is such a stupid woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.37,B2,HARUKO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without even realizing I was inside fatso, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:05.36,B2,HARUKO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she threw herself all over me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:22.06,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW) (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.52,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW) (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this woman possesses considerable Spirit Energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:28.94,B2,HARUKO (HOLLOW) (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take my time sucking her Spirit Energy from her. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.86,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.11,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.28,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.28,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.24,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,have her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:42.49,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pound you out of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.12,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.87,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Blond-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.53,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.11,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:25.18,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I promised I'd protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.46,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.50,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.13,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:55.04,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected you weren't an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:59.03,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were a Mod Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:07.00,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you first, then enjoy the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.56,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey wait! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.46,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a minute! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:10.67,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.95,B2,KON (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:21.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Getsuga...tensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:25.89,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:46.51,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... You do such crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:52.75,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Blond-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.53,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared. So scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.85,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:09.69,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this immoral scenery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:10.58,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.56,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.74,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.03,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.98,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.99,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to start a new love life with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:24.19,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.52,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:33.28,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, you said you'd protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.35,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.98,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Kon must've said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:37.86,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.30,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you trick me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:39.91,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Trick you?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.90,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:40.69,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I trusted you! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.85,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's not... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.05,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear your lame excuses
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.72,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, listen! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.59,B2,RUKIA,0000,0000,0000,,later when I have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.21,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.47,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Why are we in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.53,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.74,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:14.57,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm feeling hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.24,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.39,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.97,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,When we get home, I'll cook lots of tasty dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.77,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.86,B2,HARUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat, Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:31.95,B2,KEN,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you make is delicious, Haruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.51,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.90,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.98,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how it ends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:40.98,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,My youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:46.58,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back...my youth, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:22.55,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you get to have all the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:23.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing fun about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.91,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,She's not your type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:26.94,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Say Ichigo, you never told us your taste in girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:27.88,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of girls do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:30.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I fell in love, wouldn't that person be the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:33.67,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a hopeless romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.89,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.40,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.60,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen Court Guard Squads Rules of Cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:40.60,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}THIRTEEN COURT GUARD SQUADS RULES OF CLEANING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:41.60,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,RULE ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:45.61,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,When moving heavy objects:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:48.74,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,No Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:49.78,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,RULE TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.53,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,If an embarrassing object is found:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.66,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,No Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:57.66,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,RULE THREE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:01.75,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,When reprimanding a lazy subordinate:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:04.46,B2,GENRYUSAI,0000,0000,0000,,No Bankai!
